<section>
    <header class="page-header">
        <h1>Winter Social</h1>
    </header>

    <p><i class="fa fa-fw fa-calendar text-primary" aria-hidden="true"></i> Tuesday 26th January 2015</p>
    <p><i class="fa fa-fw fa-clock-o text-primary" aria-hidden="true"></i> <time datetime="2016-01-26 19:00">19:00</time> - <time datetime="2016-01-26 22:00">22:00</time></p>
    <p><i class="fa fa-fw fa-map-marker text-primary" aria-hidden="true"></i> PLY, 24 Lever Street, Manchester, M1 1DZ</p>

    <hr>

    <p>It's the New Year: the days are getting longer, the birds are twittering in the hedges, little leaves will soon be in the trees&hellip;</p>

    <p>Time, then, to go to the pub, to meet some fellow programmers over a drink or two. Relax and gossip about frameworks, share your gripes, wonder about the future.</p>

    <p>PLY Bar serves nice drinks in even nicer glasses, in a modern yet comfortable setting: a pleasant place to spend an evening.</p>

    <p>All are welcome.</p>

    <br>

